data.title: Star Electric String Quartet
data.text:
A high end professional electric string quartet for corporate events, parties & special events.

STAR electric string quartet specialises in corporate entertainment, media events & awards ceremonies. They are also in great demand for weddings, Bollywood events and Jewish celebrations such as Jewish weddings and Bar Mitzvahs.

Their performances feature both male and female musicians that perform on cutting edge custom made string instruments which are see through and use LED technology.

This high-impact electric string show is perfect as a feature for a corporate event, dinner or party. Everything about the performance is of the highest quality- technical mastery of the instruments, the sound, stage outfits and choreography.

Having in-house music producers and string arrangers means that the quartet have access to custom arrangements of Pop, Movie and well known classical favourites and each are given a twist to compliment the quartet’s dynamic show. Star can be a valuable addition to the entertainment for any special event and are guaranteed to impress!

The musicians studied at conservatoires in the UK and across Europe and have performed across the UK, throughout Europe and beyond.

Clients include: BBC, Cisco, Fujitsu, GSK, Rolex, UBS, Mastercard, AVIVA, UPS, Engie, PWC, , M&S, Lloyds Bank, Siemens etc…
